@mainpage Secure Source Manager API C++ Client Library

An idiomatic C++ client library for the [Secure Source Manager API][cloud-service-docs].
Secure Source Manager is a regionally deployed, single-tenant managed source
code repository hosted on Google Cloud.

While this library is **GA**, please note that the Google Cloud C++ client libraries do **not** follow
[Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/).

@tableofcontents{HTML:2}

