## Main classes

<!-- inject-client-list-start -->
The main class in this library is
[`securesourcemanager_v1::SecureSourceManagerClient`](@ref google::cloud::securesourcemanager_v1::SecureSourceManagerClient). All RPCs are exposed
as member functions of this class. Other classes provide helpers, configuration
parameters, and infrastructure to mock
[`securesourcemanager_v1::SecureSourceManagerClient`](@ref google::cloud::securesourcemanager_v1::SecureSourceManagerClient) when testing your
application.
